---
globs: lib/**/*.ts
---
- Pure functions only — same input, same output, no side effects.
- No React, no UI logic inside lib files.
- All shared types live in lib/types.ts only — no logic there.
- One file per external service.
- Calculation files must not call APIs — they receive data as parameters.
- Every function: explicitly typed params and return, wrapped in try/catch, returns null on failure (never throws).
- API wrappers: never expose raw API response shapes, always map to your own types, return Promise<YourType | null>.
